<plot>The Rex Hotel in downtown Toronto represents a timeless place where jazz music lives on. The focus of this documentary is the Classic Tuesday night jam session at the Rex - a traditional event that brings musicians from every generation to the stage. It's a place where time stops and music comes alive.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?410714</url></doc>
